NAURA Technology Group Co., Ltd. engages in the research and development, production, sale, and technical services of semiconductors in the People's Republic of China. The company offers semiconductor process equipment including etching, thin film, cleaning, heat treatment, crystal growth, and other core process equipment which are used in various applications, such as logic and memory devices, advanced packaging, third-generation semiconductors, semiconductor lighting, micro-electromechanical systems, new displays, new energy photovoltaics, substrate materials, etc. The company was formerly known as Beijing Sevenstar Electronics Co., Ltd. and changed its name to NAURA Technology Group Co., Ltd. in February 2017. NAURA Technology Group Co., Ltd. was founded in 2001 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China. ### Analyst Insights: 002371.SZ. * Levered Free Cash Flow (ttm). NAURA Technology Group Co., Ltd. Mkt Cap CNY 352.356B. ### Company Insights: 002371.SZ. 603501.SS  OmniVision Integrated Circuits Group, Inc. 603986.SS  GigaDevice Semiconductor Inc. 002475.SZ  Luxshare Precision Industry Co., Ltd. 002812.SZ  Yunnan Energy New Material (Group) Co., Ltd.



